See https://github.com/blacksphere/blackmagic/wiki

Compiling:
----------

fetch dependencies (energymicro, libopencm3) with the following command:

	git submodule update --init --recursive

build with: make

output is in ./src/blackmagic.bin


Flashing:
---------

- press "programming" button (top left) on black-magic device
- plug usb with button pressed
- minicom -D /dev/ttyACM0
- type i  (shows bootloader information)
- type u  (start upload mode)
- type CRTL-a s
- select xmodem
- select blackmagic.bin (to navigate into directory: 'space' 'space')
- type 'space' then 'enter' (starts upload, wait for completion)
- type b (boots uploaded firmware)
